CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1946, pg. 25 reads: "Summer Housewarming - Mr. and Mrs. Freeland Shaw of Kelly Street recently entertained with an elaborate housewarming. Guests included Mr. and Mrs. Chauncey Adams, The Rev. and Mrs. W.L. Shaw, Mr. and Mrs. B.F. Watkins, Mrs. Susie Huddlerton, Mrs. Sophia Douglas, Mrs. Beulah M. Shoppard, Mrs. Fannie Garreth and Mrs. Leona Dickerson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Freeland Shaw, seated at head of table, with guests including Mr. and Mrs. Chauncey Adams, The Rev. and Mrs. W.L. Shaw, Mr. and Mrs. B.F. Watkins, Susie Huddlerton, Sophia Douglas, Beulah M. Shoppard, Fannie Garreth, and Leona Dickerson, in dining room in Shaw home on Kelly Street, another version
